<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Sufism&action=edit&section=38.php.html" title="Edit section: Eastern Europe">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Eastern_Europe">Eastern Europe</span></h3>
