<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Sufism&action=edit&section=39.php.html" title="Edit section: North America">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="North_America">North America</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="Ahmed_Tijani_Ben_Omar" title="Ahmed Tijani Ben Omar">Ahmed Tijani Ben Omar</a> (b. 1950) – United States</li>
